name: Bluegrass Frog 8.5 x 11 Print
description:
This is a very beautiful giclee print of my original digital illustration.

My prints are made using genuine Epson Ultrachrome inks, which produces beautiful archival fadeless prints, and are printed on a beautiful Hahnemuhle fine art paper.

✭ Art Print Dimensions ✭

Print Size: 8.5x11 inches
Artwork Size: 

✭ Packaging of print ✭

All prints are often print to order. I allow 24 hours of drying time before packaging. 

Prints are shipped in flat custom packaging: 

① Prints are placed in protective archival cello sleeve for long-term storage.
② Print(s) are then sandwiched between 4 sheets of sturdy cardboard (2 on each side), and taped closed.
③ The cardboard sandwich is then placed inside a large cello bag for added protection.
④ Finally, the package is wrapped in packaging paper and taped on all sides to prevent any wearing along the edges.
⑤ Shipping Label and “Fragile” label are affixed to the outside package.
